kluczowych z ostatnich 65 dni. Zwracaj uwag\u0119 na trendy i wzorce, aby lepiej dostosowa\u0107 swoj\u0105 strategi\u0119 wykluczania.<\/li>\n<li><b>Strategicznie przesuwaj bud\u017cet<\/b>: B\u0105d\u017a elastyczny w zarz\u0105dzaniu bud\u017cetem reklamowym. Je\u015bli niekt\u00f3re kampanie staj\u0105 si\u0119 zbyt kosztowne lub przynosz\u0105 s\u0142abe wyniki, rozwa\u017c przeniesienie \u015brodk\u00f3w na bardziej op\u0142acalne opcje, takie jak kampanie Auto lub Broad.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Wdro\u017cenie tych strategii pozwoli Ci skuteczniej zarz\u0105dza\u0107 kampaniami PPC na Amazonie, osi\u0105gaj\u0105c lepsze wyniki przy ni\u017cszych kosztach. <br \/>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak skutecznie zarz\u0105dza\u0107 kampaniami PPC na Amazonie?<\/h1>\n<p>Chcesz zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 swoje zyski na Am<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6350,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6349","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-ecommerce"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6349"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6349"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6349\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6350"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6349"}],"wp:term":[{"ta